&lt;h5 id="anonymous_element_23"&gt;Instructions to Students&lt;/h5&gt;&#xd;
&lt;ol style="list-style-type: decimal;"&gt;&#xd;
&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Answer all&amp;nbsp;the questions.&lt;/li&gt;&#xd;
&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Put your responses in the spaces provided.&lt;/li&gt;&#xd;
&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Your responses must be&amp;nbsp;in your own words, and should be a&amp;nbsp;maximum of fifty words&amp;nbsp;in length, or two to three sentences. Q22 may require a longer answer.&lt;/li&gt;&#xd;
&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Referencing is not applicable, and any&amp;nbsp;cut and paste responses are invalid.&lt;/li&gt;&#xd;
&lt;/ol&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
